WEBVTT

00:09:01.114 --> 00:09:04.586
He also said, "I hope that these
younger veterans don't wait

00:09:04.610 --> 00:09:05.958
to get the help they need."

00:09:06.588 --> 00:09:07.874
And that's my hope, too.

00:09:09.020 --> 00:09:10.206
Because ...

00:09:11.003 --> 00:09:12.446
this life is short,

00:09:13.383 --> 00:09:16.555
and if you are fortunate enough
to have survived war

00:09:16.579 --> 00:09:18.659
or any kind of traumatic experience,

00:09:18.683 --> 00:09:22.198
you owe it to yourself
to live your life well.

00:09:22.629 --> 00:09:25.270
And you shouldn't wait
to get the training you need

00:09:25.294 --> 00:09:26.679
to make that happen.

00:09:28.663 --> 00:09:33.978
Now, the best way of ending
human suffering caused by war